sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant G as Microsoft Graph
  participant T as TS Teams Adapter
  participant R as Rust Agent Core
  participant P as Policy Engine
  participant A as Audit Log
  participant U as User (Teams)

  G->>T: Subscription validation request (validationToken)
  T-->>G: Echo validationToken plaintext

  G->>T: Change notification payload
  T->>R: SendActivity(ActivityEnvelope: action_type=WebhookNotification)
  R->>P: Evaluate(webhook_triggered_summary)
  P-->>R: allow(policy_code=WEBHOOK_ALLOWED)
  R->>A: write AuditEvent(action=webhook_received, result=success)
  R->>T: ProactiveNotify(NotifyEnvelope: summary message)
  T-->>U: Proactive Teams message

  alt subscription near expiry
    R->>G: Renew subscription
    G-->>R: renewal success
    R->>A: write AuditEvent(action=subscription_renewal, result=success)
  else renewal failure
    G-->>R: renewal error
    R->>A: write AuditEvent(action=subscription_renewal, result=failure)
  end
